    "biography": "<p>A large Awakened beaver (Castor efforderis) that digs extensive tunnels and collapses them on intruders. Russian specimens are twice the size and ferocious enough to kill a bear one-on-one.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Concealment (Personal), Enhanced Movement, Enhanced Senses (Improved Smell, Sonar)</p><p><em>Attacks: 4M, Reach −1. Habitat: In and around rivers and lakes, in wooded country. Range: Norway, Sweden, the Rhône and Elbe valleys in Germany (very rare), central Russia. The Quickness multiplier applies to both running and swimming. Book Intelligence 2/4. PAE p.25.</em></p>",
